hopobject.body: Have you got a telephone directory? can you use ibuprofen gel on piles Nick Cannon's New Year started off with a lot of pain. The 'America's Got Talent' host was hospitalized after suffering from mild kidney failure. Wife Mariah Carey took to Twitter on Jan. 4, 2012 urging fans to 'please pray for Nick as he's fighting to recover.' Carey posted a photo of herself lying alongside her husband in a hospital bed in Aspen, Colo., where they had been vacationing over the holiday season.
